00:01:18.900 --> 00:01:20.392
Some people are advised

00:01:20.390 --> 00:01:22.072
to take iron supplements.

00:01:22.408 --> 00:01:25.168
In the past, these were available only as

00:01:25.160 --> 00:01:26.744
non-heme iron.

00:01:26.740 --> 00:01:28.696
Due to the absorption process,

00:01:28.690 --> 00:01:30.440
non-heme iron can cause

00:01:30.440 --> 00:01:35.504
unpleasant effects, such as constipation.

00:01:35.500 --> 00:01:37.216
heme and non-heme iron,

00:01:37.210 --> 00:01:38.736
which increases absorption

00:01:38.730 --> 00:01:41.520
and also reduce these unwanted effects.

